TITLE: Installing React Native Vector Icons
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the react-native-vector-icons package using npm.  This is needed if you're on a vanilla React Native project, as some components use icons internally.
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstack/react-native-paper/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/01-getting-started.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install react-native-vector-icons
```

