TITLE: Babel Plugin Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure the babel plugin for React Native Paper to reduce bundle size in a React Native project. The plugin rewrites import statements to import only the used modules. This is configured in the babel.config.js file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstack/react-native-paper/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/01-getting-started.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = {
  presets: ['module:metro-react-native-babel-preset'],
  env: {
    production: {
      plugins: ['react-native-paper/babel'],
    },
  },
};
```

