TITLE: Modify package.json scripts for CRA
DESCRIPTION: This diff shows the changes to the `package.json` scripts to use `react-app-rewired` instead of `react-scripts` for `start`, `build`, and `test` commands in a Create React App project. This allows customization of the webpack configuration without ejecting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstack/react-native-paper/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/05-react-native-web.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
/* package.json */

  "scripts": {
-   "start": "react-scripts start",
+   "start": "react-app-rewired start",
-   "build": "react-scripts build",
+   "build": "react-app-rewired build",
-   "test": "react-scripts test --env=jsdom",
+   "test": "react-app-rewired test --env=jsdom"
}
```

