TITLE: Theming: Setting Material Design Version
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to specify the Material Design version (2 or 3) in the theme configuration using the `version` property.  This allows you to choose between Material Design 2 and Material You (Material Design 3).
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstack/react-native-paper/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/10-migration-guide-to-5.0.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
theme: {
  /* ... */
  version: 3 | 2
}
```

