TITLE: Babel Plugin Configuration for Expo
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure the babel plugin for React Native Paper to reduce bundle size in an Expo project.  It is configured in the babel.config.js file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/callstack/react-native-paper/blob/main/docs/docs/guides/01-getting-started.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = function(api) {
  api.cache(true);
  return {
    presets: ['babel-preset-expo'],
    env: {
      production: {
        plugins: ['react-native-paper/babel'],
      },
    },
  };
};
```

